sequenceDiagram
    participant T as Therapist App
    participant PC as Perfect Corp API
    participant HKE as Hyper-Knowledge Engine
    participant ST as Skin-Twin Engine
    participant PV as PrimeVessel IoT
    participant SZ as Skin-Zone Marketplace
    participant DB as Database

    Note over T,DB: Patient Diagnostic & Treatment Workflow

    T->>PC: 1. Capture skin images (front, left, right)
    PC->>PC: 2. Analyze images (14+ metrics)
    PC->>T: 3. Return diagnostic data
    T->>DB: 4. Store diagnostic session
    T->>HKE: 5. Request formulation recommendation
    
    HKE->>DB: 6. Query patient history
    DB->>HKE: 7. Return historical data
    HKE->>HKE: 8. Run HyperGNN inference
    HKE->>ST: 9. Send optimized parameters
    
    ST->>ST: 10. Generate formulation recipe
    ST->>HKE: 11. Return formulation
    HKE->>DB: 12. Store formulation in knowledge graph
    HKE->>T: 13. Return recommendation with confidence
    
    T->>T: 14. Therapist reviews & approves
    T->>PV: 15. Send formulation recipe (MQTT)
    
    PV->>PV: 16. Validate recipe & check inventory
    PV->>T: 17. Confirm job queued
    PV->>PV: 18. Dispense ingredients & mix
    PV->>T: 19. Report completion
    PV->>DB: 20. Log dispensing event
    
    PV->>SZ: 21. Report inventory levels
    SZ->>SZ: 22. Check reorder thresholds
    SZ->>PV: 23. Schedule ingredient delivery
    
    Note over T,DB: Follow-up & Outcome Tracking
    
    T->>PC: 24. Capture follow-up images (2-4 weeks later)
    PC->>T: 25. Return updated metrics
    T->>DB: 26. Store outcome data
    T->>HKE: 27. Submit treatment outcome
    HKE->>HKE: 28. Update knowledge graph & retrain model
    HKE->>DB: 29. Store learned insights
